title: Ep. - 381 - JENNY MCCARTHY DISCUSSES ERIKA JAYNE WOODSTOCK 99 ON HBO
description:
Jenny McCarthy discusses Erika Jayne (Girardi) this season on Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.

 

Former Philadelphia DJ Lawrence Bregman (DJ Huggy) discusses his experience at Woodstock in 99 light of the new HBO documentary Woodstock 99: Peace, Love, and Rage. The documentary tells the story of Woodstock ‘99, a music festival promoted to echo unity and counterculture idealism of the original 1969 concert, but instead devolved into riots, looting, and sexual assaults.
